Known Secrets:
1. You can change the necklace to another symbol by clicking on it.
2. Wait on scene 19 for another portal to open on the left side, click on it to get to scene 20.
3. Empty all your salt with v (the status-bar on the bottom left side should be empty) and finish the game normally. Now Elizabeth will help you fill the salt up again!
